WEBVTT

00:05:28.010 --> 00:05:33.696
In 1995, BMW paid the James Bond franchise
three million dollars

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:36.613
to have James Bond switch
from driving an Aston Martin

00:05:36.637 --> 00:05:38.257
to a BMW Z3.

00:05:39.122 --> 00:05:43.671
That one move caused so many people
to go out and buy that car,

00:05:43.695 --> 00:05:48.780
that BMW made 240 million dollars
in pre-sales alone.

00:05:49.367 --> 00:05:52.012
The year that "Brave"
and "Hunger Games" came out,

00:05:52.036 --> 00:05:55.453
female participation in archery
went up 105 percent.

00:05:55.477 --> 00:05:58.365
(Laughter)

00:05:58.389 --> 00:05:59.733
In fact, studies show

00:05:59.757 --> 00:06:03.464
that the movies you watch
don't just affect your hobbies,